description: I found cute Devin camping in the middle of nowhere. He needed some hard cash to complete his trip and I was happy to help him out. For a few bucks he really showed me what he was packin' on his hiking trip, for a few more dollars he took my package in his bearded mouth. With no one coming by, it gave me the confidence to ask if he would let me fuck him. He went for it, and so did I.
title: Devin
